290
00:16:58,840 --> 00:16:59,970
We have to record it.

291
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:01,230
Right.

292
00:17:01,670 --> 00:17:02,240
Let's go.

293
00:17:02,240 --> 00:17:03,040
Let's go.

294
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,609
