310
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:46,750
Yeah.

311
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:47,480
Let's rest here.

312
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,730
Lin Hua, what do you think?

313
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:49,570
You two rest.

314
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:50,760
I'm not tired.

315
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:51,850
I'll keep going.

316
00:17:52,310 --> 00:17:53,840
