344
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:38,200
Move a bit to the left.

345
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:40,400
Okay, right there.

346
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:41,450
Right here.

347
00:19:41,750 --> 00:19:42,480
That's good.

348
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,070
Xia Xue will stand here later.

349
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:45,110
Then you just say what you prepared—

350
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:45,880
"Time flies,

351
00:19:45,880 --> 00:19:48,070
