and Xia Xu will say, "I do."

352
00:19:48,070 --> 00:19:49,070
Alright, alright.

353
00:19:49,070 --> 00:19:51,000
I still need to change into my suit.

354
00:19:52,550 --> 00:19:53,550
I'll record a bit

355
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:54,880
for later use.

356
00:19:57,270 --> 00:19:58,250
Recording now.

357
00:19:58,790 --> 00:20:01,120
Capturing some precious moments for you.

358
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:07,480
Why is she still halfway up?

359
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,350
Did we walk that fast?

360
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:13,480
Lin Hua.

361
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,370
Something doesn't feel right.

362
00:20:16,920 --> 00:20:18,250
Let's go down and check.

363
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:20,270
Okay.

364
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,630
Xia Xue!

365
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:31,310
Xia Xue!

366
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,780
Xia Xue!

367
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,800
Xia Xue!

368
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:41,340
Xia Xue!

369
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,510
Xia Xue!

370
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,080
Split up.

371
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:23,940
Xia Xue!

372
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:27,560
Xia Xue!

373
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:32,670
Xia Xue!

374
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,200
Xia Xue!

375
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:40,520
Xia Xue!

376
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,200
Xia Xue!

377
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:47,410
Unfortunately.

378
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:50,000
I'm in a bad mood today.

379
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:52,650
But coincidentally,

380
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:56,270
you all seem to be in a good mood, huh?

381
00:23:55,580 --> 00:24:00,270
[Recording]

382
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,040
Looks like...

383
00:25:24,910 --> 00:25:26,130
it is the shipyard...

384
00:25:42,030 --> 00:25:43,290
There's an explosion!

385
00:25:45,640 --> 00:25:47,160
There are injuries.

386
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,370
There are people still inside.

387
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:54,030
There are injuries.

388
00:25:59,070 --> 00:26:00,920
Quick! Team One, secure the perimeter.

389
00:26:00,920 --> 00:26:02,440
Don't let anyone in.

390
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,000
Team Two, bring detectors

391
00:26:04,000 --> 00:26:05,330
and check for gas leaks.

392
00:26:11,110 --> 00:26:12,840
There are still people inside.

393
00:26:18,790 --> 00:26:19,960
Help save the people now.

394
00:26:19,960 --> 00:26:21,640
And compile the casualty list.

395
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:22,550
Has Mr. Ma been notified?

396
00:26:22,550 --> 00:26:23,200
Yes.

397
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,100
He's on his way.

398
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,550
Where is Young Mr. Ma?

399
00:26:26,510 --> 00:26:28,000
Ma Kai? Where is Ma Kai?

400
00:26:28,020 --> 00:26:28,750
We haven't found him yet.

401
00:26:28,750 --> 00:26:30,960
Everyone, leave this area
as soon as possible.

402
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,680
Hurry up and find him!

403
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:58,750
Hello.

404
00:26:58,750 --> 00:27:01,200
The number you dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

405
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:02,960
We now interrupt our program
for breaking news.

406
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:06,090
An explosion has occurred
at Nanping Xijiang Shipyard.

407
00:27:08,200 --> 00:27:09,690
Fire and medical teams have arrived

408
00:27:09,690 --> 00:27:11,570
at the scene
of the Nanping Xijiang Shipyard explosion

409
00:27:11,570 --> 00:27:12,920
to conduct rescue operations.

410
00:27:12,920 --> 00:27:14,680
At the site of the explosion,
authorities have implemented

411
00:27:14,680 --> 00:27:16,440
temporary traffic controls
on surrounding roads

412
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:18,400
to ensure clear access for rescue efforts.

413
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:19,430
Relevant departments have established

414
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:21,000
