415
00:27:21,000 --> 00:27:23,110
-Turn up the volume! -to coordinate
rescue and medical treatment,

416
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:26,200
and the investigation into the cause of
the incident and follow-up arrangements.

417
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:27,400
As of the time of this report,

418
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:29,000
the cause of the explosion
remains unknown,

419
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:31,070
and casualties are still being assessed.

420
00:27:31,070 --> 00:27:32,150
We will continue to follow developments

421
00:27:32,150 --> 00:27:34,030
at the Nanping Xijiang Shipyard

422
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:36,690
and bring you updates
as they become available.

423
00:27:41,260 --> 00:27:42,970
[Police]

424
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,160
Come on.

425
00:27:48,480 --> 00:27:49,200
Come on.

426
00:28:02,240 --> 00:28:03,960
They need more hands over there.

427
00:28:03,960 --> 00:28:04,880
Another one's dead.

428
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:06,310
Hurry up and carry the body over.

429
00:28:06,310 --> 00:28:07,110
Bring it here?

430
00:28:07,110 --> 00:28:07,960
Yes.

431
00:28:12,200 --> 00:28:13,860
There's another victim here.

432
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,000
Zhao Guang!

433
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:17,720
Hurry up!

434
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:19,510
Chen Adi!

435
00:28:19,850 --> 00:28:21,080
Hurry.

436
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,480
Tian Wen!

437
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,240
Hurry up.

438
00:28:23,240 --> 00:28:23,960
There are two more bodies here.

439
00:28:23,960 --> 00:28:24,720
Be careful.

440
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,960
Move the injured over there.

441
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:28,550
Okay.

442
00:28:28,890 --> 00:28:29,960
Are there many injured inside?

443
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,680
Yes.

444
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,000
You go first.

445
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:33,630
I've got this. Leave it to me.

446
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:35,140
Everyone, be careful.

447
00:28:35,170 --> 00:28:35,790
Come on.

448
00:28:35,790 --> 00:28:36,750
Watch out.

449
00:28:39,400 --> 00:28:40,060
Be careful.

450
00:28:40,110 --> 00:28:41,030
Xia Gang!

451
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:13,970
Make way.

452
00:29:25,590 --> 00:29:26,880
Ma Kai!

453
00:29:47,530 --> 00:29:53,280
[2010]

454
00:29:54,390 --> 00:29:58,430
[Police Investigation Area]

455
00:29:58,550 --> 00:29:59,350
Captain Qin,

456
00:30:00,230 --> 00:30:01,290
the results are in.

457
00:30:01,590 --> 00:30:02,110
After DNA

458
00:30:02,110 --> 00:30:02,720
comparison,

459
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,680
the tissue under Wang Bingkun's nails

460
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:06,110
doesn't belong to Lu Ming.

461
00:30:06,110 --> 00:30:08,310
He's not related to Hou Shanshan, either.

462
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:09,440
He's not her father.

463
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:11,470
Let's go.

464
00:30:12,530 --> 00:30:15,840
[Hou Jun] [Couple] [Xia Xue]

465
00:30:23,670 --> 00:30:24,510
Xia Xue.

466
00:30:26,070 --> 00:30:27,510
We didn't ask you to meet at home,

467
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:29,040
but asked you here instead.

468
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:31,160
I hope you understand our intentions.

469
00:30:31,160 --> 00:30:32,810
We just want you

470
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:34,940
to relax, let go of all your concerns,

471
00:30:35,080 --> 00:30:36,280
and be honest with us.

472
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:39,310
Don't worry. We will protect your privacy.

473
00:30:39,310 --> 00:30:41,040
I hope you can tell us the truth.

474
00:30:49,960 --> 00:30:51,350
We met ten years ago.

475
00:30:51,390 --> 00:30:54,010
[Police Office Operating Procedures]

476
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:55,550
You're Ma Kai, right?

477
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:06,200
I didn't tell Hou Jun about this.

478
00:31:06,660 --> 00:31:07,550
I don't want to cause

479
00:31:07,550 --> 00:31:10,350
unnecessary misunderstandings
between you two.

480
00:31:10,750 --> 00:31:12,550
Thanks for your consideration.

481
00:31:13,160 --> 00:31:15,090
Actually, you could have told him.

482
00:31:15,190 --> 00:31:18,110
Hou Jun and I have been married for years.

483
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,360
We don't have many secrets.

484
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:24,750
Ma Kai!

485
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:28,110
His face was charred.

486
00:31:28,110 --> 00:31:29,250
How can you be sure?

487
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,750
Most of the body was charred.

488
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:33,960
We've cross-referenced them
with the entry logs,

489
00:31:33,960 --> 00:31:34,550
and

490
00:31:34,820 --> 00:31:36,270
all the names match up.

491
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:44,060
[Ma Kai]

492
00:32:35,750 --> 00:32:38,410
You asked about
the child's biological father.

493
00:32:39,690 --> 00:32:42,290
What does that have to do
with finding my child?

494
00:32:42,320 --> 00:32:44,690
It matters. It matters a lot.

495
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:48,830
If this isn't a standard kidnapping
for ransom,

496
00:32:48,830 --> 00:32:49,920
it's very likely the child

497
00:32:49,920 --> 00:32:51,920
was taken by her biological father,

498
00:32:52,110 --> 00:32:53,030
or

499
00:32:53,030 --> 00:32:54,830
a revenge hit

500
00:32:54,830 --> 00:32:56,350
by one of his enemies.

501
00:32:56,880 --> 00:32:59,030
We've seen many cases like this.

502
00:32:59,030 --> 00:33:01,880
That's why I asked
who the biological father is,

503
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,340
but you refused to answer.

504
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,590
It's alright.

505
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:10,200
We've already traced it to Lu Ming.

506
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:17,070
Lu Ming and I...

507
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,550
did have a history.

508
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,350
But the child isn't his.

509
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,790
The kidnapping...

510
00:33:27,510 --> 00:33:28,970
has nothing to do with him.

511
00:33:31,110 --> 00:33:33,270
As for her biological father,

512
00:33:34,830 --> 00:33:37,160
that was just a mistake made in my youth.

513
00:33:44,270 --> 00:33:46,030
You two grew up together.

514
00:33:46,750 --> 00:33:47,510
So you mean,

515
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:49,370
because of that mistake you made,

516
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:51,430
you broke up with Lu Ming?

517
00:33:51,920 --> 00:33:53,960
It's not exactly something to be proud of.

518
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:56,090
If you were me, would you talk about it?

519
00:34:24,630 --> 00:34:25,889
I'll go turn myself in.

520
00:34:27,239 --> 00:34:28,510
We can't hide this.

521
00:34:29,590 --> 00:34:30,719
I'll take the blame.

522
00:34:31,969 --> 00:34:33,580
Ma Kai is Ma Derong's son.

523
00:34:34,330 --> 00:34:36,030
Do you think he'll let this go?

524
00:34:36,510 --> 00:34:38,239
What if he tries to hurt Xia Xue?

525
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:41,480
That's why I'm turning myself in.

526
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:43,480
What will happen to Xia Xue if you do?

527
00:34:43,630 --> 00:34:45,710
She needs you now more than ever.

528
00:34:52,150 --> 00:34:53,400
Even if you want to turn yourself in,

529
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:55,600
you need to make sure Xia Xue is settled.

530
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:58,200
Uncle Xia hasn't been laid to rest yet.

531
00:35:06,030 --> 00:35:06,760
Xia Xue.

532
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:09,710
Every minute you delay,

533
00:35:09,710 --> 00:35:12,150
Shanshan is in danger for another minute.

534
00:35:12,150 --> 00:35:13,920
This concerns Shanshan's safety.

535
00:35:13,920 --> 00:35:16,320
So, I hope you'll seriously consider

536
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:18,630
telling us the whole truth. Alright?

537
00:35:32,030 --> 00:35:33,320
I have nothing to hide.

538
00:36:43,150 --> 00:36:43,670
Well,

539
00:36:45,490 --> 00:36:47,290
where is the DV you brought here?

540
00:36:51,750 --> 00:36:54,430
♪ Crying in the morning ♪

541
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:57,160
♪ Tears stay ♪

542
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:00,850
♪ Oh my sleeve ♪

543
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:04,760
♪ Oh my sleeve ♪

544
00:37:05,030 --> 00:37:06,890
The police didn't just come to us.

545
00:37:07,560 --> 00:37:08,190
♪ Retreating without warning ♪

546
00:37:08,190 --> 00:37:09,590
They also went to Xia Xue.

547
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:10,750
They kept asking
about the child's background.

548
00:37:10,750 --> 00:37:12,310
♪ Would that keep on forming? ♪

549
00:37:12,960 --> 00:37:14,480
♪ Eyes low; can't believe ♪

550
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,190
Do you have any news about her?

551
00:37:20,150 --> 00:37:22,150
Don't rush. Take your time looking.

552
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,670
Don't rush.

553
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:26,400
♪ Time won't stay ♪

554
00:37:27,490 --> 00:37:30,210
♪ Dreams decay ♪

555
00:37:31,850 --> 00:37:32,330
♪ Karma spins a thread we can't unweave ♪

556
00:37:32,330 --> 00:37:33,210
No.

557
00:37:34,730 --> 00:37:35,910
Is it here?

558
00:37:38,150 --> 00:37:39,570
It should be right here.

559
00:37:39,910 --> 00:37:42,410
♪ Time won't stay ♪

560
00:37:43,530 --> 00:37:44,080
♪ Dreams decay ♪

561
00:37:44,080 --> 00:37:45,370
Why is it gone?

562
00:37:46,700 --> 00:37:47,880
Could someone have picked it up?

563
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:48,690
♪ Karma spins a thread we can't unweave ♪

564
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:50,160
If someone picked it up,

565
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:51,950
the body might also be found.

566
00:37:56,750 --> 00:38:00,370
♪ Oh ♪

567
00:38:02,290 --> 00:38:02,960
♪ The thread won't shape
the soul I became ♪

568
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:04,360
We have to hurry

569
00:38:12,050 --> 00:38:15,200
♪ Don't look back my way ♪

570
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:19,460
♪ I won't hear your name ♪

571
00:38:20,210 --> 00:38:22,940
♪ Let the voice start to fade ♪

572
00:38:24,350 --> 00:38:27,310
♪ I won't play your wicked game ♪

573
00:38:29,230 --> 00:38:33,560
♪ Can't go forward; can't go back ♪

574
00:38:37,170 --> 00:38:44,230
